OL,3,CTributes to 'star pupil' who died in
OL,4,Criver tragedy
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to a "much
OL,7,Floved" 13-year-old girl who died after
OL,8,Fbeing pulled from a North Yorkshire
OL,9,Friver.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,12,FRiver Wharfe near Burnsall in the
OL,13,FSkipton area after Palwasha Akbar was
OL,14,Freported missing at around 6.30pm on
OL,15,FSunday 31 May.
OL,17,FNorth Yorkshire Police said she was
OL,18,Fpulled from the water and taken to
OL,19,Fhospital by air ambulance. She died in
OL,20,Fhospital.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
