OL,3,CTributes to 'star pupil' who died in
OL,4,Criver tragedy
OL,6,FBronte Girls' Secondary Academy, in
OL,7,FBradford, paid tribute to Palwasha.
OL,9,FActing principal Lyndsay Hall said:
OL,10,F"We are deeply saddened by the death
OL,11,Fof one of our much-loved students in a
OL,12,Fswimming accident. She was a valued
OL,13,Fand much-loved member of the school
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,F"She was one of our star pupils and
OL,17,Fwill be remembered for her compassion
OL,18,Fand willingness to go above and beyond
OL,19,Fto help others.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780765560
OL,3,CTributes to 'star pupil' who died in
OL,4,Criver tragedy
OL,6,F"All our thoughts and prayers are with
OL,7,Fher family, friends and everyone
OL,8,Faffected by this tragic loss at this
OL,9,Fincredibly difficult time."
OL,11,FThe school is offering pastoral care
OL,12,Fand wellbeing support as the incident
OL,13,Fhas had a significant impact on
OL,14,Fstudents, staff and the wider
OL,15,Fcommunity.
OL,17,FThe acting headteacher said more
OL,18,Finformation would follow about the
OL,19,Fschool's plans to pay tribute to the
OL,20,Fteenager.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
