OL,3,CTributes to 'star pupil' who died in
OL,4,Criver tragedy
OL,6,FThere have been a number of tragic
OL,7,Fincidents involving water during
OL,8,Frecent hot weather across Yorkshire.
OL,10,FOn Wednesday, the body of 11-year-old
OL,11,FMackenzie Swift was found after a four
OL,12,Fday search after he disappeared in the
OL,13,FRiver Don.
OL,15,FOn Bank Holiday Monday, sixteen-year-
OL,16,Fold Muhammed Secka died after entering
OL,17,Fthe Rother Valley Country Park in
OL,18,FSouth Yorkshire.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
