OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780765560
OL,3,CTributes to 'star pupil' who died in
OL,4,Criver tragedy
OL,6,FOn the same day, 13-year-old Reco
OL,7,FPuttock, got into difficulty in a
OL,8,Freservoir in Halifax. He was taken to
OL,9,Fhospital where he later died.
OL,11,FA day earlier, 15-year-old Declan
OL,12,FSawyer died after entering a lake in
OL,13,FLincoln.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/5
